 0415                        instance.TypeDefinition = declaration.TypeDefinition;
 416                    }
 417                }
 418            }
 419
 420            // check for missing name or id.
 0421            if (node.SymbolicId.IsNullOrEmpty() &&
 0422                node.SymbolicName.IsNullOrEmpty() &&
 0423                string.IsNullOrEmpty(node.BrowseName)) {

 0425                    (parent?.SymbolicId.Name ?? "No Parent"));

 0438                        name.Append(NodeDesign.kPathChar);
 0439                        continue;
 440                    }
 0441                    if (char.IsLetterOrDigit(c) || c == NodeDesign.kPathChar[0]) {

 444                    }

 452            }

 0455            ValidateAndAssignBrowseName(node);
 0456            ValidateAndAssignSymbolicId(node, parent);

 458
 459            // add a display name.
 0460            if (node.DisplayName == null) {

 0462                    Value = node.BrowseName,
 0463                    Key = $"{node.SymbolicId.Name}_DisplayName",
 0464                    IsAutogenerated = true
 0465                };
 0466            }
 467            else {
 0468                if (node.DisplayName.Value != null) {
 0469                    node.DisplayName.Value = node.DisplayName.Value.Trim();

 0471                if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(node.DisplayName.Key)) {
 0472                    node.DisplayName.Key = $"{node.SymbolicId.Name}_DisplayName";
 473                }
 474            }

 0479                    node.Description.Value = node.Description.Value.Trim();
 480                }

 769        /// <summary>
 770        /// Imports a list of parameters.
 771        /// </summary>
 772        private bool ImportParameters(NodeDesign node, Parameter[] parameters, string parameterType) {
 0773            if (parameters == null || parameters.Length == 0) {
 0774                return false;
 775            }
 776
 0777            var id = 0;
 0778            foreach (var parameter in parameters) {
 0779                parameter.Parent = node;
 780
 781                // check name.
 0782                if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(parameter.Name)) {
 0783                    throw new FormatException(
 0784                        $"The node has a parameter without a name: {node.SymbolicId.Name}.");
 785                }
 786
 0787                var name = parameter.Name;
 788                // assign an id.
 0789                if (parameter.IdentifierSpecified) {
 0790                    id = parameter.Identifier;
 0791                }
 0792                else if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(parameter.BitMask)) {
 793
 0794                    if (ulong.TryParse(parameter.BitMask, NumberStyles.AllowHexSpecifier,
 0795                        CultureInfo.InvariantCulture, out var mask)) {
 0796                        var bytes = BitConverter.GetBytes(mask);
 0797                        parameter.Identifier = BitConverter.ToInt32(bytes, 0);
 0798                        parameter.IdentifierSpecified = true;
 799                    }
 800                }
 801
 0802                if (!parameter.IdentifierSpecified) {
 0803                    parameter.Identifier = ++id;
 0804                    parameter.IdentifierSpecified = true;
 805                }
 806
 807                // update id if specified in name.
 0808                var index = name.LastIndexOf(NodeDesign.kPathChar[0]);
 809
 0810                if (index != -1) {
 0811                    foreach (var c in name) {
 0812                        if (!char.IsDigit(c)) {
 0813                            index = -1;
 0814                            break;
 815                        }
 816                    }
 0817                    if (index != -1) {
 0818                        id = parameter.Identifier = Convert.ToInt32(name.Substring(index + 1));
 0819                        parameter.IdentifierInName = true;
 820                    }
 821                }
 822
 823                // add a description.
 0824                if (parameter.Description == null) {
 0825                    parameter.Description = new LocalizedText {
 0826                        Value = string.Format("A description for the {0} {1}.",
 0827                        parameter.Name, parameterType.ToLower()),
 0828                        IsAutogenerated = true
 0829                    };
 830                }
 831
 0832                if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(parameter.Description.Key)) {
 0833                    parameter.Description.Key = string.Format("{0}_{1}_{2}_Description",
 0834                        node.SymbolicId.Name, parameterType, parameter.Name);
 835                }
 836
 837                // add a datatype.
 0838                if (parameter.DataType.IsNullOrEmpty()) {
 0839                    parameter.DataType = Constants.BaseDataType;
 840                }
 841            }
 0842            return true;
 843        }

 845        // 2nd pass - validate and expand node design
 846
 847        /// <summary>
 848        /// Creates instance nodes out of standard components such as
 849        /// encodings or method args.
 850        /// </summary>
 851        /// <param name="model"></param>
 852        private void ValidateNodes(ModelDesign model) {
 0853            var hasDataTypesDefined = false;
 0854            var hasMethodsDefined = false;
 855
 856            // Validate each node in the model
 0857            foreach (var node in model.Items) {
 0858                if (node is DataTypeDesign) {
 0859                    hasDataTypesDefined = true;
 860                }
 0861                if (node is MethodDesign) {
 0862                    hasMethodsDefined = true;
 863                }
 0864                Validate(node);
 865            }
 866
 867            // Add method argument property children
 0868            if (hasMethodsDefined) {
 0869                foreach (var node in model.Items) {
 0870                    if (node is MethodDesign methodDesign) {
 0871                        AddMethodArguments(methodDesign);
 872                    }
 873                }
 874            }
 875
 876            // Add additional nodes to the model
 0877            var nodes = new List<NodeDesign>(model.Items);
 0878            if (hasDataTypesDefined) {

 923        /// <summary>
 924        /// Validates the type.
 925        /// </summary>
 926        private void ValidateType(TypeDesign type) {
 927            switch (type) {
 928                case VariableTypeDesign variableType:
 0929                    variableType.DataTypeNode = (DataTypeDesign)FindNode(variableType.DataType,
 0930                        typeof(DataTypeDesign), type.SymbolicId.Name);
 931
 932                    // TODO: Is this DecodeValue=
 0933                    if (variableType.DefaultValue != null) {
 0934                        var decoder = new XmlDecoder(variableType.DefaultValue, _context);
 0935                        variableType.DecodedValue = decoder.ReadVariantContents(out var typeInfo);
 0936                        if (typeInfo != null) {
 0937                            variableType.ValueRank = (typeInfo.ValueRank == ValueRanks.Scalar) ?
 0938                                ValueRank.Scalar : ValueRank.Array;
 0939                            variableType.ValueRankSpecified = true;
 940                        }
 0941                        decoder.Close();
 942                    }
 943
 0944                    if (variableType.BaseTypeNode != null) {
 0945                        var baseType = variableType.BaseTypeNode as VariableTypeDesign;
 0946                        if (baseType.DataType != Constants.BaseDataType) {
 0947                            if (variableType.DataType == Constants.BaseDataType) {
 0948                                variableType.DataType = baseType.DataType;
 0949                                variableType.DataTypeNode = baseType.DataTypeNode;
 950                            }
 0951                            if (baseType.DataType != variableType.DataType) {
 0952                                throw new FormatException(
 0953                                    $"Subtype cannot redefine the datatype. {type.SymbolicId.Name}");
 954                            }
 955                        }
 956                    }
 957                    break;
 958                case DataTypeDesign dataType:
 0959                    ValidateParameters(dataType, dataType.Fields);
 0960                    dataType.IsStructure =
 0961                        IsTypeOf(dataType, Constants.Structure);
 0962                    dataType.IsUnion =
 0963                        IsTypeOf(dataType, Constants.Union);
 0964                    dataType.IsEnumeration =
 0965                        IsTypeOf(dataType, Constants.Enumeration) || dataType.IsOptionSet;
 0966                    dataType.BasicDataType =
 0967                        GetBasicDataType(dataType);
 0968                    if (!dataType.IsStructure) {
 0969                        if (dataType.HasEncodings) {
 0970                            throw new FormatException(
 0971                                $"Encodings but not a structure: {type.SymbolicId.Name}");
 972                        }
 0973                        if (dataType.IsEnumeration) {
 0974                            if (!dataType.HasFields && !dataType.IsAbstract) {
 0975                                throw new FormatException(
 0976                                    $"Enumeration type with no fields: {type.SymbolicId.Name}");
 977                            }
 978                        }
 979                        else {
 0980                            if (dataType.HasFields && !dataType.IsOptionSet) {
 0981                                throw new FormatException(
 0982                                    $"Simple type with fields defined: {type.SymbolicId.Name}");
 983                            }
 984                        }
 985                    }
 986                    else {
 987                        // add encodings.
 0988                        if (!dataType.HasEncodings) {
 0989                            dataType.Encodings = new EncodingDesign[] {
 0990                                CreateEncoding(dataType, Constants.DefaultXml),
 0991                                CreateEncoding(dataType, Constants.DefaultBinary),
 0992                                CreateEncoding(dataType, Constants.DefaultJson)
 0993                            };
 0994                            dataType.HasEncodings = true;
 0995                        }
 996                        else {
 997                            // check for duplicates.
 0998                            var encodings = new Dictionary<XmlQualifiedName, EncodingDesign>();
 0999                            foreach (var encoding in dataType.Encodings) {
 01000                                if (encodings.ContainsKey(encoding.SymbolicName)) {
 01001                                    throw new FormatException("The datatype has a duplicate encoding " +
 01002                                        $"defined: {dataType.SymbolicId.Name} {encoding.SymbolicName.Name}");
 1003                                }
 01004                                encodings.Add(encoding.SymbolicName, encoding);
 1005                            }
 1006                        }
 1007                    }
 1008                    break;
 1009            }
 01010        }

 1012        /// <summary>
 1013        /// Determines the basic type for a datatype.
 1014        /// </summary>
 1015        /// <param name="dataType"></param>
 1016        /// <returns></returns>
 1017        private static BasicDataType GetBasicDataType(DataTypeDesign dataType) {
 01018            if (dataType == null) {
 01019                return BasicDataType.BaseDataType;
 1020            }
 1021            // check if it is a built in data type.
 01022            if (dataType.SymbolicName.Namespace == Namespaces.OpcUa) {

 01024                    if (name == dataType.SymbolicName.Name) {
 01025                        return (BasicDataType)Enum.Parse(typeof(BasicDataType),
 01026                            dataType.SymbolicName.Name);
 1027                    }
 1028                }

 01031                return BasicDataType.Enumeration;
 1032            }

 01034            var basicType = GetBasicDataType(dataType.BaseTypeNode as DataTypeDesign);
 1035            // data type is user defined if a sub-type of structure.
 01036            if (basicType == BasicDataType.Structure) {
 01037                return BasicDataType.UserDefined;
 1038            }
 01039            return basicType;
 1040        }

 01086                    IsAutogenerated = true

 1264        /// <summary>
 1265        /// Add enumeration strings
 1266        /// </summary>
 1267        /// <param name="dataType"></param>
 1268        private void AddEnumStrings(DataTypeDesign dataType) {
 01269            var children = new List<InstanceDesign>();
 1270
 01271            if (dataType.Children != null && dataType.Children.Items != null) {
 01272                children.AddRange(dataType.Children.Items);

 01275                return;

 01279                var last = 0;
 01280                for (var index = 0; index < 32; index++) {
 01281                    var hit = 1 << index;

 01284                            while (last++ < index) {
 01285                                values.Add(new Ua.LocalizedText(string.Empty, "Reserved"));
 1286                            }

 01288                            last = index + 1;
 01289                            break;
 1290                        }
 1291                    }
 1292                }

 01294                    values.ToArray(), children);
 01295            }
 1296            else {

 01298                var sequential = true;
 01299                foreach (var parameter in dataType.Fields) {
 01300                    if (parameter.Identifier != index) {
 01301                        sequential = false;
 01302                        break;
 1303                    }
 01304                    index++;
 1305                }
 01306                if (sequential) {

 1310                    }

 1723        // 3rd pass - create instance hierarchy
 1724
 1725        private Hierarchy CreateInstanceHierarchy(NodeDesign root) {
 01726            SetOverriddenNodes(root);
 1727
 1728            // collect all of the nodes that define the hierachy.
 01729            var nodes = new List<HierarchyNode>();
 01730            var references = new List<HierarchyReference>();
 01731            BuildInstanceHierarchy(root, nodes, references);
 1732
 01733            var hierarchy = new Hierarchy {
 01734                References = references
 01735            };
 1736
 01737            var rootId = root.SymbolicId;
 1738
 1739            // add root node.
 01740            var instance = root as InstanceDesign;
 1741
 01742            if (instance == null) {
 01743                rootId = new XmlQualifiedName(root.SymbolicId.Name + "Instance",
 01744                    root.SymbolicId.Namespace);
 1745            }
 1746
 01747            var rootNode = new HierarchyNode {
 01748                RelativePath = string.Empty
 01749            };
 1750
 01751            if (instance == null || instance.TypeDefinitionNode == null) {
 01752                rootNode.Instance = CreateMergedInstance(root, rootId, string.Empty);
 01753            }
 1754            else {
 01755                rootNode.Instance = CreateMergedInstance(instance.TypeDefinitionNode, rootId,
 01756                    string.Empty);
 1757
 01758                if (root.SymbolicName == rootNode.Instance.SymbolicName) {
 01759                    rootNode.Instance.BrowseName = root.BrowseName;
 01760                    rootNode.Instance.DisplayName = root.DisplayName;
 1761                }
 01762                ((InstanceDesign)rootNode.Instance).MergeIn(root);
 1763            }
 1764
 01765            rootNode.ExplicitlyDefined = false;
 1766
 01767            hierarchy.Nodes.Add(string.Empty, rootNode);
 01768            hierarchy.NodeList.Add(rootNode);
 1769
 1770            // build instance hierachy.
 01771            foreach (var node in nodes) {
 01772                var explicitlyDefined = false;
 01773                for (var parent = node.Instance; parent != null; parent = parent.Parent) {
 01774                    if (parent.SymbolicId == root.SymbolicId) {
 01775                        explicitlyDefined = true;
 01776                        break;
 1777                    }
 1778                }

 2165        /// <summary>

 2170        /// <param name="reference"></param>
 2171        /// <returns></returns>
 2172        private HierarchyReference TranslateReference(string currentPath, XmlQualifiedName sourceId,
 2173            Reference reference) {

 2227
 02228            for (var index = 1; index < sourcePath.Length; index++) {
 02229                if (index > currentPathParts.Length) {
 02230                    return mergedReference;
 2231                }
 2232
 02233                if (currentPathParts[currentPathParts.Length - index] != sourcePath[sourcePath.Length - index]) {
 02234                    targetRoot = new string[currentPathParts.Length - index];
 02235                    Array.Copy(currentPathParts, 0, targetRoot, 0, targetRoot.Length);
 02236                    break;
 2237                }
 2238            }
 2239
 2240            // no common root.
 02241            if (targetRoot == null && currentPathParts.Length > sourcePath.Length) {
 02242                targetRoot = new string[currentPathParts.Length - sourcePath.Length];
 02243                Array.Copy(currentPathParts, 0, targetRoot, 0, targetRoot.Length);
 2244            }
 2245
 02246            var builder = new StringBuilder();
 02247            if (targetRoot != null) {
 02248                foreach (var item in targetRoot) {
 02249                    if (builder.Length > 0) {
 02250                        builder.Append(NodeDesign.kPathChar);
 2251                    }
 02252                    builder.Append(item);
 2253                }
 2254            }
 02255            if (targetPath != null) {
 02256                foreach (var item in targetPath) {
 02257                    if (builder.Length > 0) {
 02258                        builder.Append(NodeDesign.kPathChar);
 2259                    }
 02260                    builder.Append(item);
 2261                }
 2262            }
 2263
 02264            mergedReference.TargetId = null;
 02265            mergedReference.TargetPath = builder.ToString();
 2266
 02267            return mergedReference;
 2268        }
 2269

 2271        /// <summary>
 2272        /// Build instance hierarchy
 2273        /// </summary>

 2283                case InstanceDesign instance:

 2289        /// <summary>
 2290        /// Create node model
 2291        /// </summary>
 2292        /// <param name="root"></param>
 2293        /// <param name="namespaceUris"></param>
 2294        private void CreateNode(NodeDesign root, NamespaceTable namespaceUris) {
 02295            if (root is InstanceDesign) {
 02296                root.Model = CreateNode(root.Hierarchy.NodeList[0].Instance, null, string.Empty,
 02297                    root.Hierarchy, false, false, namespaceUris);
 02298                if (root.Model is InstanceNodeModel instance) {
 02299                    instance.ClearModellingRules(_context.ToSystemContext());
 2300                }
 02301            }
 2302            else {
 02303                root.Model = CreateNode(root, null, string.Empty,
 02304                    root.Hierarchy, true, true, namespaceUris);
 2305            }
 2306
 02307            if (root.Hierarchy != null && root is TypeDesign) {
 02308                if (root.Hierarchy.Nodes.TryGetValue(string.Empty, out var hierarchyNode)) {
 02309                    if (hierarchyNode.Identifier != null) {
 02310                        if (hierarchyNode.Identifier is uint) {
 02311                            hierarchyNode.Instance.NumericId = (uint)hierarchyNode.Identifier;
 02312                            hierarchyNode.Instance.NumericIdSpecified = false;
 02313                        }
 02314                        else if (hierarchyNode.Identifier is string) {
 02315                            hierarchyNode.Instance.StringId = (string)hierarchyNode.Identifier;
 2316                        }
 2317                    }
 02318                    root.Instance = hierarchyNode.Instance.Model = CreateNode(
 02319                        hierarchyNode.Instance, null, string.Empty, root.Hierarchy,
 02320                        false, false, namespaceUris);
 02321                    if (hierarchyNode.Instance.Model is InstanceNodeModel instance) {
 02322                        instance.ClearModellingRules(_context.ToSystemContext());
 2323                    }
 2324                }
 2325            }
 02326        }
 2327
 2328        /// <summary>
 2329        /// Create node model
 2330        /// </summary>
 2331        /// <param name="nodeDesign"></param>
 2332        /// <param name="parent"></param>
 2333        /// <param name="basePath"></param>
 2334        /// <param name="hierarchy"></param>
 2335        /// <param name="explicitOnly"></param>
 2336        /// <param name="isTypeDefinition"></param>
 2337        /// <param name="namespaceUris"></param>
 2338        /// <returns></returns>
 2339        private BaseNodeModel CreateNode(NodeDesign nodeDesign, BaseNodeModel parent, string basePath,
 2340            Hierarchy hierarchy, bool explicitOnly, bool isTypeDefinition, NamespaceTable namespaceUris) {
 2341
 2342            // Create node model
 02343            var nodeModel = CreateNode(nodeDesign, parent, namespaceUris);
 02344            nodeModel.SymbolicName = nodeDesign.SymbolicName.Name;
 02345            nodeModel.NodeId = nodeDesign.GetNodeId(namespaceUris);
 02346            nodeModel.BrowseName = new QualifiedName(nodeDesign.BrowseName,
 02347                (ushort)namespaceUris.GetIndex(nodeDesign.SymbolicName.Namespace));
 02348            nodeModel.DisplayName = new Ua.LocalizedText(nodeDesign.DisplayName.Key,
 02349                string.Empty, nodeDesign.DisplayName.Value);
 02350            if (nodeDesign.Description != null && !nodeDesign.Description.IsAutogenerated) {
 02351                nodeModel.Description = new Ua.LocalizedText(nodeDesign.Description.Key,
 02352                    string.Empty, nodeDesign.Description.Value);
 2353            }
 02354            nodeModel.WriteMask = AttributeWriteMask.None;
 02355            nodeModel.UserWriteMask = AttributeWriteMask.None;
 2356
 02357            if (nodeModel is MethodNodeModel method) {
 02358                var design = (MethodDesign)nodeDesign;
 02359                if (design.MethodDeclarationNode != null) {
 02360                    method.TypeDefinitionId = design.MethodDeclarationNode.GetNodeId(namespaceUris);
 2361                }
 2362            }
 02363            if (hierarchy == null) {
 02364                return nodeModel;
 2365            }
 2366
 2367            // Build references for node
 02368            foreach (var reference in hierarchy.References) {
 02369                if (reference.SourcePath != basePath &&
 02370                    reference.TargetPath != basePath) {
 2371                    continue;
 2372                }
 02373                var referenceTypeId = CreateNodeId(reference.ReferenceType, namespaceUris);
 02374                var isInverse = reference.IsInverse;
 02375                if (reference.TargetId != null) {
 02376                    var targetId = CreateNodeId(reference.TargetId, namespaceUris);
 02377                    nodeModel.AddReference(referenceTypeId, isInverse, targetId);
 02378                    continue;
 2379                }
 02380                if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(reference.TargetPath)) {
 02381                    if (parent != null) {
 02382                        nodeModel.AddReference(referenceTypeId, isInverse, parent.NodeId);
 02383                        continue;
 2384                    }
 2385                }
 02386                if (reference.SourcePath == basePath) {
 02387                    if (!hierarchy.Nodes.TryGetValue(reference.TargetPath, out var target)) {
 2388                        continue;
 2389                    }
 02390                    if (!target.ExplicitlyDefined && isTypeDefinition) {
 2391                        continue;
 2392                    }
 02393                    var targetId = target.Instance.GetNodeId(namespaceUris);
 02394                    nodeModel.AddReference(referenceTypeId, isInverse, targetId);
 02395                    continue;
 2396                }
 2397
 02398                if (!hierarchy.Nodes.TryGetValue(reference.SourcePath, out var source)) {
 2399                    continue;
 2400                }
 02401                if (!source.ExplicitlyDefined && isTypeDefinition) {
 2402                    continue;
 2403                }
 2404
 02405                var sourceId = source.Instance.GetNodeId(namespaceUris);
 02406                nodeModel.AddReference(referenceTypeId, !isInverse, sourceId);
 2407            }
 2408
 2409            // Add child nodes from hierarchy
 02410            foreach (var node in hierarchy.NodeList) {
 02411                if (explicitOnly) {
 02412                    if (!node.ExplicitlyDefined) {
 2413                        continue;
 2414                    }
 2415                }
 02416                var childPath = node.RelativePath;
 2417                // only looking for nodes in the current tree (part of the base path).
 02418                if (!childPath.StartsWith(basePath, StringComparison.Ordinal)) {
 2419                    continue;
 2420                }
 2421                // ignore reference to the current base node.
 02422                if (childPath == basePath) {
 2423                    continue;
 2424                }
 2425                // relative should always end in the name of the current instance.
 02426                if (!childPath.EndsWith(node.Instance.SymbolicName.Name, StringComparison.Ordinal)) {
 2427                    continue;
 2428                }
 2429                // get the parent path which is without our name at the end.
 02430                if (childPath.Length > node.Instance.SymbolicName.Name.Length) {
 02431                    var parentPath = node.RelativePath
 02432                        .Substring(0, childPath.Length - node.Instance.SymbolicName.Name.Length - 1);
 02433                    if (parentPath != basePath) {
 02434                        continue;
 2435                    }
 2436                }
 2437                else {
 02438                    if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(basePath)) {
 2439                        // Error?
 2440                        continue;
 2441                    }
 2442                }
 2443
 02444                if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(basePath)) {
 02445                    childPath = childPath.Substring(basePath.Length + 1);
 02446                    childPath = string.Format("{0}{1}{2}", basePath, NodeDesign.kPathChar, childPath);
 2447                }
 2448
 2449                // Follow the modelling rules
 02450                if (!explicitOnly) {
 02451                    if (node.Instance is InstanceDesign instanceDesign) {
 02452                        if (!node.ExplicitlyDefined &&
 02453                            instanceDesign.ModellingRule != ModellingRule.Mandatory) {
 02454                            if ((instanceDesign.ModellingRule != ModellingRule.None &&
 02455                                 instanceDesign.ModellingRule != ModellingRule.ExposesItsArray &&
 02456                                 instanceDesign.ModellingRule != ModellingRule.OptionalPlaceholder &&
 02457                                 instanceDesign.ModellingRule != ModellingRule.MandatoryPlaceholder) ||
 02458                                 !isTypeDefinition) {
 2459                                continue;
 2460                            }
 2461                        }
 2462                    }
 2463                }
 2464
 2465                // Create child node model
 02466                node.Instance.Model = CreateNode(node.Instance, nodeModel, childPath, hierarchy,
 02467                    false, isTypeDefinition, namespaceUris);
 2468
 2469                // Add nodes based on modelling rule modelling rules
 02470                if (node.Instance.Model is InstanceNodeModel instance) {
 02471                    if (explicitOnly) {
 02472                        if (node.ExplicitlyDefined) {
 02473                            nodeModel.AddChild(instance);
 2474                        }
 02475                    }
 02476                    else if (isTypeDefinition) {
 02477                        if (instance.ModellingRuleId == ObjectIds.ModellingRule_Mandatory) {
 02478                            nodeModel.AddChild(instance);
 02479                        }
 02480                        else if (node.ExplicitlyDefined &&
 02481                            instance.ModellingRuleId == ObjectIds.ModellingRule_Optional) {
 02482                            nodeModel.AddChild(instance);
 02483                        }
 02484                        else if (node.ExplicitlyDefined && (
 02485                            instance.ModellingRuleId == ObjectIds.ModellingRule_ExposesItsArray ||
 02486                            instance.ModellingRuleId == ObjectIds.ModellingRule_OptionalPlaceholder ||
 02487                            instance.ModellingRuleId == ObjectIds.ModellingRule_MandatoryPlaceholder)) {
 02488                            nodeModel.AddChild(instance);
 2489                        }
 02490                    }
 2491                    else {
 02492                        if (instance.ModellingRuleId == ObjectIds.ModellingRule_Mandatory) {
 02493                            nodeModel.AddChild(instance);
 02494                        }
 02495                        else if (node.ExplicitlyDefined &&
 02496                            instance.ModellingRuleId == ObjectIds.ModellingRule_Optional) {
 02497                            nodeModel.AddChild(instance);
 2498                        }
 2499                    }
 2500                }
 2501            }
 02502            return nodeModel;
 2503        }

 2505        /// <summary>
 2506        /// Convert single node design to node model
 2507        /// </summary>
 2508        /// <param name="node"></param>
 2509        /// <param name="parent"></param>
 2510        /// <param name="namespaceUris"></param>
 2511        /// <returns></returns>
 2512        private BaseNodeModel CreateNode(NodeDesign node, BaseNodeModel parent, NamespaceTable namespaceUris) {
 2513            switch (node) {
 2514                case ObjectTypeDesign objectTypeDesign:
 02515                    return new ObjectTypeNodeModel {
 02516                        Handle = objectTypeDesign,
 02517                        IsAbstract = objectTypeDesign.IsAbstract,
 02518                        SuperTypeId = objectTypeDesign.BaseTypeNode?.GetNodeId(namespaceUris)
 02519                    };
 2520                case VariableTypeDesign variableTypeDesign:
 02521                    var variableNode = new DataVariableTypeNodeModel {
 02522                        Handle = variableTypeDesign,
 02523                        IsAbstract = variableTypeDesign.IsAbstract,
 02524                        SuperTypeId = variableTypeDesign.BaseTypeNode?.GetNodeId(namespaceUris)
 02525                    };
 02526                    if (variableTypeDesign.Hierarchy != null &&
 02527                        variableTypeDesign.Hierarchy.Nodes.TryGetValue(string.Empty, out var instance) &&
 02528                        instance.Instance is VariableDesign mergedInstance) {
 02529                        var (valueRank, dimensions) = mergedInstance.ValueRank.ToStackValue(
 02530                            mergedInstance.ArrayDimensions);
 02531                        variableNode.Value = mergedInstance.DecodedValue == null ? (Variant?)null :
 02532                            new Variant(mergedInstance.DecodedValue);
 02533                        variableNode.DataType = mergedInstance.DataTypeNode.GetNodeId(namespaceUris);
 02534                        variableNode.ValueRank = valueRank;
 02535                        variableNode.ArrayDimensions = dimensions?.ToArray();
 02536                    }
 2537                    else {
 02538                        var (valueRank, dimensions) = variableTypeDesign.ValueRank.ToStackValue(
 02539                            variableTypeDesign.ArrayDimensions);
 02540                        variableNode.Value = variableTypeDesign.DecodedValue == null ? (Variant?)null :
 02541                            new Variant(variableTypeDesign.DecodedValue);
 02542                        variableNode.DataType = variableTypeDesign.DataTypeNode.GetNodeId(namespaceUris);
 02543                        variableNode.ValueRank = valueRank;
 02544                        variableNode.ArrayDimensions = dimensions?.ToArray();
 2545                    }
 02546                    return variableNode;
 2547                case ReferenceTypeDesign referenceTypeDesign:
 02548                    return new ReferenceTypeNodeModel {
 02549                        Handle = referenceTypeDesign,
 02550                        IsAbstract = referenceTypeDesign.IsAbstract,
 02551                        Symmetric = referenceTypeDesign.Symmetric,
 02552                        InverseName = referenceTypeDesign.Symmetric ? Ua.LocalizedText.Null :
 02553                            new Ua.LocalizedText(referenceTypeDesign.InverseName.Key, string.Empty,
 02554                            referenceTypeDesign.InverseName.Value),
 02555                        SuperTypeId = referenceTypeDesign.BaseTypeNode?.GetNodeId(namespaceUris)
 02556                    };
 2557                case ObjectDesign objectDesign:
 02558                    return new ObjectNodeModel(parent) {
 02559                        Handle = node,
 02560                        TypeDefinitionId = objectDesign.TypeDefinitionNode.GetNodeId(namespaceUris),
 02561                        ReferenceTypeId = CreateNodeId(
 02562                            objectDesign.ReferenceType, namespaceUris),
 02563                        ModellingRuleId = objectDesign.ModellingRule.ToNodeId(),
 02564                        EventNotifier = objectDesign.SupportsEvents ?
 02565                            EventNotifiers.SubscribeToEvents : EventNotifiers.None,
 02566                        NumericId = objectDesign.NumericIdSpecified ? objectDesign.NumericId : 0u
 02567                    };
 2568                case PropertyDesign propertyDesign:
 02569                    var pacl = propertyDesign.AccessLevel.ToStackValue();
 02570                    var (pvalueRank, pdimensions) = propertyDesign.ValueRank.ToStackValue(
 02571                        propertyDesign.ArrayDimensions);

 02575                        ReferenceTypeId = CreateNodeId(
 02576                            propertyDesign.ReferenceType, namespaceUris),
 02577                        ModellingRuleId = propertyDesign.ModellingRule.ToNodeId(),
 02578                        NumericId = propertyDesign.NumericIdSpecified ? propertyDesign.NumericId : 0u,
 02579                        DataType = propertyDesign.DataTypeNode.GetNodeId(namespaceUris),
 02580                        ValueRank = pvalueRank,
 02581                        ArrayDimensions = pdimensions?.ToArray(),

 02585                        Historizing = propertyDesign.Historizing,
 02586                        Value = DecodeValue(propertyDesign, namespaceUris)
 02587                    };
 2588                case VariableDesign variableDesign:
 02589                    var vacl = variableDesign.AccessLevel.ToStackValue();
 02590                    var (vvalueRank, vdimensions) = variableDesign.ValueRank.ToStackValue(
 02591                        variableDesign.ArrayDimensions);
 02592                    return new DataVariableNodeModel(parent) {
 02593                        Handle = node,
 02594                        TypeDefinitionId = variableDesign.TypeDefinitionNode.GetNodeId(namespaceUris),
 02595                        ReferenceTypeId = CreateNodeId(
 02596                            variableDesign.ReferenceType, namespaceUris),
 02597                        ModellingRuleId = variableDesign.ModellingRule.ToNodeId(),

 02600                        DataType = variableDesign.DataTypeNode.GetNodeId(namespaceUris),
 02601                        ValueRank = vvalueRank,
 02602                        ArrayDimensions = vdimensions?.ToArray(),
 02603                        AccessLevel = vacl,
 02604                        UserAccessLevel = vacl,
 02605                        MinimumSamplingInterval = variableDesign.MinimumSamplingInterval,

 02608                    };
 2609                case DataTypeDesign dataTypeDesign:
 02610                    return new DataTypeNodeModel {
 02611                        Handle = dataTypeDesign,

 02613                        Purpose = (Nodeset.Schema.DataTypePurpose)(int)dataTypeDesign.Purpose,
 02614                        Definition = DecodeDataTypeDefinition(dataTypeDesign, namespaceUris),
 02615                        SuperTypeId = dataTypeDesign.BaseTypeNode?.GetNodeId(namespaceUris)

 2617                case MethodDesign methodDesign:
 02618                    return new MethodNodeModel(parent) {
 02619                        Handle = methodDesign,
 02620                        TypeDefinitionId = null,

 2627                case ViewDesign viewDesign:

 02635            return null;

 2638        /// <summary>
 2639        /// Decode value from variable design
 2640        /// </summary>
 2641        /// <param name="variableDesign"></param>
 2642        /// <param name="namespaceUris"></param>
 2643        /// <returns></returns>
 2644        private Variant? DecodeValue(VariableDesign variableDesign, NamespaceTable namespaceUris) {
 02645            var value = variableDesign.DecodedValue;
 2646            switch (value) {
 2647                case ExtensionObject extensionObject:
 02648                    SetExtensionObjectTypeId(extensionObject, namespaceUris);
 02649                    break;
 2650                case ExtensionObject[] listOfExtensionObjects:

 02667                            new XmlQualifiedName(name, namespaceUri), namespaceUris);

 02672                return null;
